1. Install nginx controler
kubectl apply -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kubernetes/ingress-nginx/controller-v1.2.0/deploy/static/provider/cloud/deploy.yaml

2. Install cert-manager
https://cert-manager.io/v1.1-docs/installation/kubernetes/#installing-the-kubectl-plugin

3. Need register free DNS (freenom.com)

4. Configurung DNS in Cloud (Azure,AWS,GCP)
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OKvOvHuOnrw&ab_channel=storagefreak

5. Configuring lensencrypt-prod.yaml

6. Deploy deployment.yaml and service.yaml

7. Configuring and deploy Ingress.yaml


Enjoy!